text: Jefrey Payeras (born October 16, 1993) is an American-born Guatemalan soccer player who currently plays for C.S.D. Municipal in the Liga Nacional. In August 2016, Payeras made his debut for Guatemala in a friendly 0–0 tie against Panama. ==Honors== ;C.S.D.
